ies to Winnipeg and thence to Sit ka Alaska It costs the state approximately 8000000 an nually to maintain this system The railroads of the country last year bought materials sup plies and fuel amounting to 900000000 in 12174 cities and towns in 2637 counties in 48 states of the Union The 81 counties out of 87 in Minnesota and their 291 cities and towns shared in the distribution of this immense sum During 1929 and 1930 railway pur chases of the necessities men tioned averaged 1184000000 annually In the five years from 1931 to 1935 this yearly average dropped to 559819 800 These figures were re cently presented to a special"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2024-01-04T04:18:42.185Z", "group": ["ndnp/mnhi", "minnesota-historical-society-saint-paul-mn-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn90059182/1938-03-10/ed-1/?sp=4", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:mnhi:batch_mnhi_motocross_ver01:data:sn90059182:00513689548:1938031001:0092/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg#h=302&w=221", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:mnhi:batch_mnhi_motocross_ver01:data:sn90059182:00513689548:1938031001:0092/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=604&w=443", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/mnhi/batch_mnhi_motocross_ver01/data/sn90059182/00513689548/1938031001/0092.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "location": ["saint louis", "ely", "saint louis county", "minnesota", "united states"], "location_city": ["ely"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["saint louis"], "location_state": ["minnesota"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "application/json", "text/plain"], "number": ["sn90059182", "3", "0", "0000000004", "9", "6", "8", "1", "4", "5"], "number_edition": ["1"], "number_lccn": ["sn90059182"], "number_page": ["0000000004"], "number_reel": ["0", "0", "5", "1", "